properties.value: Tentacle may refer to any of the following:

content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Tentacle

Tentacle may refer to any of the following:

  • Tentacle (Temple Trekking) - A monster fought during the Temple Trekking minigame.
  • Enormous Tentacle - A monster that is part of the Kraken's body.
  • Tentacle pool - A pool that can be built in the oubliette in a player-owned house.
  • Kraken tentacle - An item obtained as a drop from Cave krakens and its boss variant.
  • Abyssal tentacle - An weapon created by combining an abyssal whip with a kraken tentacle.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
